    public interface Cartesian<A,B,P extends Cartesian<?,?,P>>
extends Profunctor<A,B,P>
    Profunctor strength in the cartesian product sense: p a b -> p (c ^ a) (c ^ b) for any type c.
    See Also:
    Fn1, Cocartesian
